                                <layout style="vertical" rend="arris_up">The ogham inscription is <q>on the left angle (A/D) towards the top of the stone, reading upwards.</q> <q>Towards the bottom of the face is a roman-letter, Latin inscription in two horizontal lines</q> (Edwards 2007, 394).</layout>
